Package builder

This is the builder package, which contains the AppBuilder object along with all the controller and boundary objects necessary to use it.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppBuilder
    Main class for the Builder app.
    ChooseTileController
    A MouseListener controller for choosing tiles to be selectable when building a board in AppBuilder.
    CtrlChangeLevelName
    ActionListener controller for setting or changing the name of a level being created in an AppBuilder object.
    CtrlDeleteLevel
    ActionListener controller for deleting a level that was being built in an AppBuilder object.
    CtrlExitWithoutSaving
    ActionListener controller for exiting the builder without saving one's work on a level.
    CtrlModifyLevel
    ActionListener controller to handle bringing up the level building view based on user's selection of which level to modify.
    CtrlModifyTargetScore
    ActionListener controller for modifying the scores required in a level to reach each star threshold.
    CtrlPreview
    ActionListener controller for previewing a level in the builder as it will look when saved.
    CtrlSaveLevel
    Saves a level to ASCII file format as specified by Grant.
    CtrlSubmitWords
    ActionListener controller for saving user's submitted words to ThemeLevel's Dict.
    ViewBuildLevel
    Created by billyzs on 12/3/16.
    ViewMenu
    Created by billyzs on 11/30/16.
    ViewPreview
    Created by billyzs on 12/8/16.
    ViewWelcome
    Created by billyzs on 11/30/16.
